{"tid":1382371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢多日 前線有野講","createTime":"2019-07-29T12:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T12:53:07.000Z","uid":149104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"75d6c8976f1d2a3bb2ee8a7f00232d18267f0007","tid":1382371,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:49:26.000Z","msg":"發左咁多日夢 次次都見到有人掉頭盔 水 眼罩<br />\n兄弟手足 物資已經缺乏 唔好咩都掉出去啦 <br />\n物資組買物資要錢 運送要承擔風險 但一下就俾你掉左出去 <br />\n我學生一個每次都會買物資去 已經窮到要日日食飯盒 但為左各位手足嘅安全 我覺得食飯盒食一世都冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次見到狗前面有頭盔就想衝出去汁番番黎 但又驚俾佢一槍爆頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但最近見到狗仔槍槍爆人頭 連頭盔都凹埋 我就諗如果手足喺前線冇頭盔會唔會有生命危險 <br />\n雖然好驚 而且都中過彈 但為左手足汁得一個得一個 錢唔重要 生命先最重要 <br />\n希望前線有齊曬裝備先好上 狗仔已經冇曬人性 <br />\n亦唔希望見到有人受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記住各位手兄發完夢裝備唔要 唔好掉 記得攞番去物資站 依家物資愈黎愈少同貴 唔好再亂掉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n學生哥已經頂唔順 想休息啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n光復香港 時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日發夢嘅學生哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50e91fabd420861ccd700666c0d6678d97ec7e07","tid":1382371,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:49:38.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f414d43bc9bf49d1cd96fd59c9fc9d574e643b15","tid":1382371,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:49:51.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"22d6bc791003ea3bb7f74a8316e9b7badafcabd3","tid":1382371,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:50:07.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1bbdbdd59f705ccb02ee0f0b495b160a58ce54c4","tid":1382371,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:50:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"20c8da2cbf06be848cc8e4fcf29c0c9d48244663","tid":1382371,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:51:04.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ab3a60da5b434fafb7744994e45fa69f1ba60bfd","tid":1382371,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:51:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"18be9823dfbe3b11eb5cf88e120669c9551ef0ee","tid":1382371,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:51:42.000Z","msg":"Push推到前線入黎睇"},{"pid":"18b9804f146e66705e594083dfa8e42185549056","tid":1382371,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:51:54.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"99c8475cf3f8d173b64a8e5e25fc01077ee65133","tid":1382371,"uid":149104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T12:53:07.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}